template: SELECT MIN(aka_title.id) AS aka_title_id, MIN(title.production_year) AS title_production_year, MIN(char_name.name) AS char_name_name FROM char_name, aka_title, title, cast_info, name, movie_companies WHERE cast_info.person_id = name.id AND cast_info.movie_id = title.id AND cast_info.person_role_id = char_name.id AND aka_title.movie_id = title.id AND movie_companies.movie_id = title.id AND title.production_year BETWEEN 1955 AND 2000 AND cast_info.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice: Japanese version)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') AND name.name_pcode_cf BETWEEN 'A' AND 'F' AND title.episode_nr > %s AND name.gender = %s AND title.production_year < %s AND movie_companies.note LIKE %s AND name.name LIKE %s;
